snippet.title: Digital ez LG rom test [Download available]
snippet.description:
With the hard searching work and all the programming work of КукуРуку (Giant Thanks). Here is reborn of Digital ez LG game pack from LG RT-21FB20VW model. 

Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AUitCGlnr4_t8yDzycU6meD3dCGz0jd-/view?usp=sharing (info in readme)
